    "MissionGiver": "MicroTech",
    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: SMALL CARGO RESCUE",
    "Description": "It seems that a contractor of ours had an issue with their delivery and abandoned their cargo over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.\n\nThis cargo is incredibly important to the resource drive and we need them recovered.\n\nOnce you\u2019re ready, head over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> with the appropriate equipment (like a <EM4>tractor beam</EM4>) and retrieve the cargo. Expect to find between <EM4>50-55 SCU</EM4> of various box sizes. \n\nAlso, in order to guarantee the cargo\u2019s safety, be on the lookout for any hostiles in the area. Once secured, deliver the resources to a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. My colleagues will secure it.\n\nYou may even find that the cargo ship is still operational, so if you have another pilot with you, it may be worth using that ship to deliver everything. We\u2019ll leave that decision with you.\n\nKind Regards,\n\n\nAster Remmington\nContractor Liaison Officer\nmicroTech",
